 wp-att-573579\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-28-810x541.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with marble countertops, wooden cabinets, and an island. A vase with branches stands on the island. Large window offers a snowy outdoor view.\" width=\"810\" height=\"541\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-28-810x541.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-28-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-28-768x513.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-28.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573578\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573578\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-30-810x542.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with wooden cabinets, marble countertops, and a sink by a window. Framed artworks hang on a wall, and a glimpse of an open living area with a hanging lamp is visible.\" width=\"810\" height=\"542\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-30-810x542.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-30-800x536.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-30-768x514.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-30.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573583\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573583\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-23-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with wooden cabinets and marble countertops. Open shelving displays glassware. Long dining table with chairs on the left, large window and bar chairs on the right.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-23-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-23-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573587\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573587\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-19-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Room with high ceiling, wooden beams, large windows with curtains, and a table surrounded by white upholstered chairs. Natural light fills the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-19-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-19-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe residence focuses on a broader discourse regarding luxury and sustainability within the context of mountain architecture. Where earlier mountain homes often emphasized rustic materials in visually heavy compositions, this project employs natural elements with a lighter touch, allowing the surrounding landscape to provide the primary visual impact through those generously proportioned metal-clad windows.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://desig