lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-14-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A wooden coffee table with stacked books, a ceramic plate, and two decorative figurines on top.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-14-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573594\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573594\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-11-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Living room with a stone fireplace, large mirror above, wicker basket, wooden coffee table with books, and a vase of flowers.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-11-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-11-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-11-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-11-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=573598\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-573598\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/04/studio-mountain-hml-2-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A sunlit corner with a wooden bench covered by a furry throw